name: BespokenToken
description: BKT & BTX Are Binance Smart Chain Tokens for Project Bespoken. BKT Tokens Are Being Issued Pre-Launch of The Project's Utility - Coin Flips. Coin Flips Deepen The Trade Types Available To Users Trading In Crypto Futures.  Dually Used As Reward Tokens, BKT & BTX Are Used To Reward Trader Activity For Participation In The Finance Fee Fundraising Pool, Made Available To A Short List Of Pre-Launched Projects
